  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's exactly the point.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Ponary.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ponary.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's where most of the Jews of Vilna were killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, I don't-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't remember that strongly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It might have been.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It might have been.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- I just-- you know, the reason I am saying it might have been-- I cannot-- cannot-- after-- you know, afterwards when you start thinking that to permit something like that in the German occupation, to sing something like that in the ghetto, it-- you would kind of think like it's crazy that every-- that-- that they would permit something like that.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yet, as I told you, I saw there once a performance showing [HEBREW] with a-- with a shield, with a [YIDDISH] David-- the yellow-- and a sword in his hand fighting the Romans.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean-- which-- and obviously the allegory is to the-- to the Germans-- the Romans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here that this great warrior, [HEBREW] from biblical times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I wouldn't be surprised that maybe that went through and nobody paid attention, and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I know I learned it in-- in-- in-- in-- in Vilna, and I sang it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I sang it in the camps later, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
